00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:42.570
So what we're going
to learn is called

00:01:42.570 --> 00:01:44.790
alternate nostril breathing.

00:01:44.790 --> 00:01:47.100
It sounds just like what it is.

00:01:47.100 --> 00:01:51.120
All we're going to be doing
is breathing alternately

00:01:51.120 --> 00:01:52.320
through each nostril.

00:01:52.320 --> 00:01:54.660
It has a nice calming effect.

00:01:54.660 --> 00:01:58.560
This is something that you can
do if you have high anxiety

00:01:58.560 --> 00:02:01.897
or you're feeling a
little bit nervous.

00:02:01.897 --> 00:02:03.730
It's just a nice, quick
breathing technique.

00:02:03.730 --> 00:02:05.090
So what we're going
to be doing is

00:02:05.090 --> 00:02:06.810
we're going to be
taking our index finger

00:02:06.810 --> 00:02:08.610
and our middle
finger, and we're just

00:02:08.610 --> 00:02:10.860
going to be placing them
in between our eyebrows

00:02:10.860 --> 00:02:13.590
right here.

00:02:13.590 --> 00:02:14.470
It's pretty simple.

00:02:14.470 --> 00:02:16.950
And then we're going to take
our thumb and ring finger,

00:02:16.950 --> 00:02:19.533
and these two are actually going
to be the ones that are going

00:02:19.533 --> 00:02:20.855
to be closing off our nostrils.

00:02:20.855 --> 00:02:22.650
So what we're all
going to do first

00:02:22.650 --> 00:02:27.180
is take a normal breath
in through our nose,

00:02:27.180 --> 00:02:28.630
and breathe out
through the nose.

00:02:31.410 --> 00:02:32.890
Let's do that one more time.

00:02:32.890 --> 00:02:40.156
Breathing in through the
nose and exhaling out.

00:02:40.156 --> 00:02:42.530
So now, what we're going to
do is close our right nostril

00:02:42.530 --> 00:02:45.610
with our thumb, and inhale
through the left nostril.

00:02:49.940 --> 00:02:52.130
Switching, exhaling
out through the right.

00:02:56.098 --> 00:03:03.590
In through the right,
and now through the left.

00:03:03.590 --> 00:03:06.590
And you can close your eyes, if
you're comfortable doing that.

00:03:06.590 --> 00:03:12.320
In through the left, and
out through the right.

00:03:15.308 --> 00:03:19.090
Now, you can just continue
on your own at your own pace,

00:03:19.090 --> 00:03:20.943
taking nice deep breaths.

00:03:20.943 --> 00:03:24.887
