00:03:54.990 --> 00:03:57.300
See if you can make the
breaths just a little deeper.

00:04:21.450 --> 00:04:24.620
And keeping the eyes closed,
you can drop your hand.

00:04:24.620 --> 00:04:26.330
Just rest it in your lap.

00:04:26.330 --> 00:04:28.313
Return to normal breathing.

00:04:36.050 --> 00:04:38.050
I want you to think
of one thing that you

00:04:38.050 --> 00:04:39.570
are grateful for in your life.

00:05:02.220 --> 00:05:05.430
And slowly and gradually,
you may open your eyes

00:05:05.430 --> 00:05:06.180
