one, and kind of that's

00:56:57.850 --> 00:57:01.270
shown here tonight by all of
you coming out and supporting

00:57:01.270 --> 00:57:04.120
this film and
supporting these topics.

00:57:04.120 --> 00:57:05.560
And that's the important part.

00:57:05.560 --> 00:57:07.330
That's how we get
into businesses.

00:57:07.330 --> 00:57:08.830
That's how we make lives change.

